name: #06 The Star
description:
A naked bird kneels by the water; one foot is in the water and one foot is on the land. Above her head is one large star, representing her core essences, and smaller stars, representing the chakras. In each hand she holds a jug. From one jug she pours a liquid into the water. From the other jug she pours a fire onto the land.

from Arcana Collection
